==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hemidactyl
<hw>Hem`i*dac"tyl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Hemi-</er>, and <er>Dactyl</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any
species of Old World geckoes of the genus <gen>Hemidactylus</gen>. The
hemidactyls have dilated toes, with two rows of plates
beneath.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

